                          <li>
                              <span>Bảy</span>
                              <a href="#" title=""><i class="fas fa-cloud-sun-rain"></i></a>
                              <em>26°</em>
                          </li>
                          <li>
                              <span>C.Nhật</span>
                              <a href="#" title=""><i class="fas fa-cloud-sun"></i></a>
                              <em>30°</em>
                          </li>
                      </ul>
                  </div>
                  
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="advertisment-box">
              <figure>
                  <a href="#" title="Advertisment">
                      <img src="/assets/images/homes/hinhads01.gif" alt="">
                  </a>
              </figure>
          </div>
      </aside>
      <aside class="order-lg-3 col-lg-3 order-md-2 col-md-6 col-xs-12 order-2">
          <div class="widget whitish low-opacity">
              <div style="background-image: url(/assets/images/homes/hinhbirthday.png)" class="bg-image"></div>
              <div class="dob-head">
                  <img src="/assets/images/homes/anh-bia.webp" alt="">
                  <div class="dob">
                      <i>07</i>
                      <span>Tháng Tư</span>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="dob-meta">
                  <h6>Hôm nay là sinh nhật của <a href="#" title="">Duy Tân</a></h6>
                  <p>Hãy gửi lời chúc mừng sinh nhật đến họ.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
      </aside>
  </div>
</div>
